<br>
Please explain to us Temu how it is that so many married middle aged, mid to upper educated, mid to upper income, many ex-military and many self employed (the predominant demographics of conservatives) are so much unaware, are so unable to understand, are so ignorant and brainwashed. Please explain to us how you and a few others became enlightened and more knowledgeable than this group to the point of hating anyone who represents their political beliefs. Was it from a long life of experience? Special schools of advanced awareness? Or is it what you have been told to believe?<br>
